---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import PageHead from "../../components/PageHead.astro";
import Tooltip from "../../components/Tooltip.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="It's Not You - It Might Be Your Machine"
  description="A quick checklist to help you troubleshoot common knitting machine issues—without blaming yourself."
>
  <div class="page-wrap troubleshoot-page-wrap">
    <header class="lm-hero">
   
      <div class="lm-hero__text">
        <h1>It's Not You — It Might Be Your Machine</h1>
        <p>
          When something goes wrong on a knitting machine, most knitters assume they did something wrong.
          Sometimes that's true - but many times the machine just needs a quick check.
        </p>
      </div>
    </header>
<!-- Funnel callout: non-member — styled panel inviting users to explore membership -->
<section data-ms-content="!members" class="lm-membership-callout" aria-labelledby="lm-membership-heading">
  <h2 id="lm-membership-heading" class="lm-membership-callout__headline">Need help?</h2>
  <div class="lm-membership-callout__body">
    <p>If the checklist didn't solve it, you don't have to figure it out alone.</p>
    <p>Knit it Now members have access to troubleshooting guides, tutorials, and machine-specific help so you can quickly track down what's going wrong.</p>
  </div>
  <p class="lm-membership-callout__cta-wrap">
    <a href="/membership" class="lm-membership-callout__cta" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Knit it Now Membership</a>
  </p>
</section>

<!-- Funnel callout: member -->
<section data-ms-content="members" class="lm-callout" style="margin: 18px 0 22px;">
  <strong>Thank you for being a member.</strong>
  <p style="margin: 10px 0 0;">
    You have access to the deeper troubleshooting resources when you need them.
  </p>
</section>



    <div class="lm-well">
    <div class="lm-reset" aria-label="60-second reset">
      <h2>The 60-Second Reset</h2>
      <ul class="lm-resetList">
        <li><strong>Re-thread</strong> the yarn in the tension unit and carriage and make sure it feeds smoothly.</li>
        <li><strong>Reset</strong> the carriage to <Tooltip term="plain knitting">plain knitting </Tooltip> settings.</li>
        <li><strong>Test</strong> 10 rows with a smooth "known good" yarn.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>You'd be surprised how often that alone fixes the problem.</p>
    </div>

    <section aria-label="5 things to check">
      <h2>5 Things to Check Before Blaming Your Machine</h2>

      <div class="lm-steps">
      <div class="lm-step">
        <div class="lm-step__header">
          <span class="lm-step__badge">1</span>
          <h3 class="lm-step__title">Yarn Path</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="lm-step__body">
          <div class="lm-stepGrid">
            <div class="lm-stepGrid__media">
              <figure class="lm-photo">
                <div class="lm-photo__label">What to look for</div>
                <img
                  src="/images/yarn-path.jpg"
                  alt="Yarn path example near the mast/tension area"
                  loading="lazy"
                />
                <figcaption>Yarn that snags, twists, or tightens suddenly can cause "mystery" drops.</figcaption>
              </figure>
            </div>
            <div class="lm-stepGrid__text">
              <p>If the yarn snags or feeds unevenly, the machine can't form consistent stitches. Even a small twist in the tension unit can cause dropped stitches.</p>
              <p><strong>You're looking for:</strong> yarn that feeds unevenly, jerks while knitting, or suddenly tightens.</p>
              <p><strong>Quick test:</strong> Pull the yarn gently and watch the full path to the needles.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="lm-divider" />

      <div class="lm-step">
        <div class="lm-step__header">
          <span class="lm-step__badge">2</span>
          <h3 class="lm-step__title">Needle Movement</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="lm-step__body">
          <div class="lm-stepGrid">
            <div class="lm-stepGrid__media">
              <div class="lm-mediaSpacer" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="lm-stepGrid__text">
              <p>Every needle should slide freely. One sticky or bent needle can cause problems in the same spot again and again.</p>
              <p><strong>You're looking for:</strong> a needle that feels sticky, bent, or doesn't slide as smoothly as the others.</p>
              <p><strong>Quick test:</strong> Slide the needles by hand and feel for resistance.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="lm-divider" />

      <div class="lm-step">
        <div class="lm-step__header">
          <span class="lm-step__badge">3</span>
          <h3 class="lm-step__title">Sponge Bar Pressure</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="lm-step__body">
          <div class="lm-stepGrid">
            <div class="lm-stepGrid__media">
              <figure class="lm-photo">
                <div class="lm-photo__label">What to look for</div>
                <img
                  src="/images/sponge-bar.jpg"
                  alt="Close-up of removing or inspecting the sponge bar"
                  loading="lazy"
                />
                <figcaption>Loose needles often point to sponge bar pressure.</figcaption>
              </figure>
            </div>
            <div class="lm-stepGrid__text">
              <p>A worn <Tooltip term="sponge bar">sponge bar</Tooltip> is one of the most common causes of mysterious knitting issues. If needles feel loose, the machine can't hold stitches reliably.</p>
              <p><strong>You're looking for:</strong> needles that feel loose, sit lower than normal, or don't stay firmly in position.</p>
              <p><strong>Quick test:</strong> Do the needles sit firmly in position?</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="lm-divider" />

      <div class="lm-step">
        <div class="lm-step__header">
          <span class="lm-step__badge">4</span>
          <h3 class="lm-step__title">Carriage Settings</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="lm-step__body">
          <div class="lm-stepGrid">
            <div class="lm-stepGrid__media">
              <div class="lm-mediaSpacer" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="lm-stepGrid__text">
              <p>Sometimes a patterning setting is left on accidentally. One tiny lever can completely change how the machine knits.</p>
              <p><strong>You're looking for:</strong> a <Tooltip term="tuck">Tuck</Tooltip>, <Tooltip term="slip">Slip</Tooltip>, or <Tooltip term="holding position">Hold</Tooltip> button that may have been engaged accidentally.</p>
              <p><strong>Quick test:</strong> Reset everything to plain knit settings and try again.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="lm-divider" />

      <div class="lm-step">
        <div class="lm-step__header">
          <span class="lm-step__badge">5</span>
          <h3 class="lm-step__title">Yarn Compatibility</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="lm-step__body">
          <div class="lm-stepGrid">
            <div class="lm-stepGrid__media">
              <figure class="lm-photo">
                <div class="lm-photo__label">What to look for</div>
                <img
                  src="/images/yarn-path.jpg"
                  alt="Close-up of yarn types that may be fuzzy or uneven"
                  loading="lazy"
                />
                <figcaption>Fuzzy or uneven yarn can "fight" the machine even when you're doing everything right.</figcaption>
              </figure>
            </div>
            <div class="lm-stepGrid__text">
              <p>Not every yarn behaves well on a knitting machine. Thick, fuzzy, or uneven yarns can create trouble even when you're doing everything right.</p>
              <p><strong>You're looking for:</strong> yarn that is fuzzy, uneven, thick, or hard for the machine to pull consistently.</p>
              <p><strong>Quick test:</strong> Try a smooth "known good" yarn to see if the problem disappears.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="note" aria-label="Reassurance">
      <h2>Remember This</h2>
      <p><strong>You didn't break your machine — and you're not alone.</strong></p>
      <p>
        Machine knitting has a lot of moving parts. Most issues come down to yarn flow, needle movement,
        or a setting that's easy to overlook.
      </p>
    </section>

    <hr class="lm-hairline" />
    <section class="lm-safetynet" aria-label="Still stuck safety net">
      <h2>Still stuck?</h2>
      <p>
        If none of the above solved the problem, it might be time for a pro to take a look. I keep a running list of <a href="/repairs" target="_blank">known repair shops</a> if you need a place to start.</p>
    </section>

    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Sticky CTA banner: non-members only; shown after scroll, dismissible (sessionStorage) -->
  <aside
    data-ms-content="!members"
    id="lm-sticky-banner"
    class="lm-sticky-banner"
    aria-label="Membership reminder"
    aria-hidden="true"
    role="complementary"
  >
    <div class="lm-sticky-banner__inner">
      <p class="lm-sticky-banner__message">Need more help?</p>
      <div class="lm-sticky-banner__actions">
        <a
          href="https://www.knititnow.com/subscribe/plans.cfm"
          class="lm-sticky-banner__cta"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          Knit it Now Membership →
        </a>
        <button
          type="button"
          class="lm-sticky-banner__dismiss"
          aria-label="Dismiss banner"
          title="Dismiss"
        >
          <span aria-hidden="true">×</span>
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </aside>

  <style>
    /* Override global .page-wrap top padding; Layout already supplies header clearance */
    .troubleshoot-page-wrap.page-wrap { padding-top: 8px; }

    /* Membership callout: panel with soft background, left accent, and clear CTA */
    .lm-membership-callout {
      margin: 18px 0 22px;
      padding: 24px 24px 28px;
      background: rgba(82, 104, 45, 0.06);
      border: 1px solid rgba(82, 104, 45, 0.18);
      border-left: 4px solid #52682d;
      border-radius: 14px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    }
    .lm-membership-callout__headline {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      line-height: 1.3;
      color: #243015;
    }
    .lm-membership-callout__body {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .lm-membership-callout__body p {
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #374151;
    }
    .lm-membership-callout__body p:last-child {
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .lm-membership-callout__cta-wrap {
      margin: 0;
    }
    .lm-membership-callout__cta {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 20px;
      background: #52682d;
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 10px;
      transition: background 0.2s ease, transform 0.15s ease;
    }
    .lm-membership-callout__cta:hover {
      background: #445626;
      color: #fff;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }
    .lm-membership-callout__cta:focus-visible {
      outline: 2px solid #52682d;
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }

    .lm-well{
      background:#fff;
      border-radius:18px;
      padding:34px;
      margin-top:18px;
      box-shadow:0 14px 36px rgba(0,0,0,.10);
    }

    .lm-hero{
      display:flex;
      gap:14px;
      align-items:flex-start;
      margin-bottom:16px;
      padding-top:0.5rem;
    }
    .lm-hero__logo{
      flex:0 0 auto;
    }
    .lm-hero__text h1{
      margin-top:0;
    }

    .lm-reset{
      border:1px solid rgba(82,104,45,.22);
      border-left:4px solid #52682d;
      background:rgba(82,104,45,.06);
      border-radius:12px;
      padding:18px 20px;
      margin-bottom:22px;
    }
    .lm-reset h2{
      margin-top:0;
      margin-bottom:6px;
    }
    .lm-resetList{
      list-style:none;
      padding-left:0;
      margin:12px 0;
    }
    .lm-resetList li{
      position:relative;
      padding-left:26px;
      margin:6px 0;
    }
    .lm-resetList li::before{
      content:"✔";
      position:absolute;
      left:0;
      top:0;
      font-weight:700;
      color:#52682d;
      opacity:.85;
    }

    .lm-stepGrid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(240px, 360px) 1fr;
      gap:18px;
      align-items:center;
    }
    .lm-stepGrid__media{
      display:flex;
      justify-content:flex-start;
    }
    .lm-stepGrid__text{
      min-width:0;
    }
    .lm-mediaSpacer{
      width:100%;
      max-width:340px;
      min-height:220px;
      visibility:hidden;
    }

    .lm-photo{
      margin:0 !important;
      margin-top:0 !important;
      align-self:start !important;
      max-width:340px;
      justify-self:start;
      border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.12);
      border-radius:14px;
      overflow:hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.10);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.7);
    }
    .lm-photo__label{
      font-weight:700;
      padding:10px 12px;
      border-bottom:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.10);
    }
    .lm-photo img{
      display:block;
      width:100%;
      height:auto;
      object-fit:cover;
    }
    .lm-photo figcaption{
      padding:10px 12px 12px;
      opacity:.85;
      font-size:0.95rem;
    }

    .lm-steps{
      position:relative;
      padding-left:14px;
    }
    .lm-steps::before{
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      left:6px;
      top:10px;
      bottom:10px;
      width:2px;
      background:rgba(82,104,45,.18);
    }
    .lm-step{
      position:relative;
      border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.10);
      border-radius:14px;
      overflow:hidden;
      background:#fff;
      margin: 14px 0;
    }
    .lm-step__badge{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      width:28px;
      height:28px;
      border-radius:999px;
      background:#fff;
      color:#52682d;
      font-weight:700;
      font-size:.9rem;
    }
    .lm-step__header{
      background:#52682d;
      color:#fff;
      padding:14px 18px;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:12px;
      margin-left:6px;
    }
    .lm-step__title{
      margin:0;
      font-size:1.1rem;
      line-height:1.3;
      color:#fff !important;
    }
    .lm-step__body{
      padding:14px;
    }
    .lm-divider{
      border:0;
      border-top:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.08);
      margin:14px 0;
    }

    .lm-hairline{
      border:0;
      border-top:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.10);
      margin:18px 0;
    }
    .lm-safetynet h2{
      margin-top:0;
    }
    .lm-safetynet a{
      color:#52682d;
      font-weight:700;
      text-decoration:underline;
      text-underline-offset: 2px;
    }
    .lm-safetynet a:hover{
      text-decoration-thickness: 2px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 820px){
      .lm-stepGrid{
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap:12px;
      }
      .lm-mediaSpacer{
        display:none;
      }
      .lm-photo{
        max-width:420px;
        justify-self:stretch;
      }
      .lm-step__header{ padding:12px; }
      .lm-step__body{ padding:12px; }
      .lm-well{
        padding:22px;
      }
    }

    /* --- Sticky membership banner: compact toast-style (non-members, scroll-triggered) --- */
    .lm-sticky-banner {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      padding: 0 16px calc(28px + env(safe-area-inset-bottom, 0));
      pointer-events: none;
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(100%);
      transition: opacity 0.35s ease, transform 0.35s ease;
    }
    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      .lm-sticky-banner {
        transition: none;
      }
    }
    .lm-sticky-banner.lm-sticky-banner--visible {
      pointer-events: auto;
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
    .lm-sticky-banner__inner {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 10px 16px;
      padding: 10px 14px 10px 16px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.98);
      border: 1px solid rgba(82, 104, 45, 0.16);
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08), 0 0 0 1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
    }
    .lm-sticky-banner__message {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 0.9375rem;
      line-height: 1.35;
      color: #243015;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .lm-sticky-banner__actions {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .lm-sticky-banner__cta {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 8px 14px;
      background: #52682d;
      color: #fff;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.875rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: background 0.2s ease, transform 0.15s ease;
    }
    .lm-sticky-banner__cta:hover {
      background: #445626;
      color: #fff;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }
    .lm-sticky-banner__cta:focus-visible {
      outline: 2px solid #52682d;
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }
    .lm-sticky-banner__dismiss {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      width: 28px;
      height: 28px;
      padding: 0;
      border: none;
      background: transparent;
      color: #9ca3af;
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      line-height: 1;
      cursor: pointer;
      border-radius: 6px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      transition: color 0.2s ease, background 0.2s ease;
    }
    .lm-sticky-banner__dismiss:hover {
      color: #6b7280;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }
    .lm-sticky-banner__dismiss:focus-visible {
      outline: 2px solid #52682d;
      outline-offset: 2px;
    }
    @media (max-width: 520px) {
      .lm-sticky-banner {
        padding-left: 12px;
        padding-right: 12px;
      }
      .lm-sticky-banner__inner {
        flex-direction: row;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 10px 12px;
        gap: 10px;
      }
      .lm-sticky-banner__message {
        width: 100%;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .lm-sticky-banner__actions {
        justify-content: center;
      }
    }
  </style>
  <script is:inline>
    (function () {
      var STORAGE_KEY = "troubleshoot-sticky-banner-dismissed";
      var SHOW_AFTER_PX = 350;
      var HIDE_ABOVE_PX = 220;
      var banner = document.getElementById("lm-sticky-banner");
      if (!banner || sessionStorage.getItem(STORAGE_KEY) === "1") return;
      function setVisible(visible) {
        if (visible) {
          banner.classList.add("lm-sticky-banner--visible");
          banner.setAttribute("aria-hidden", "false");
        } else {
          banner.classList.remove("lm-sticky-banner--visible");
          banner.setAttribute("aria-hidden", "true");
        }
      }
      function onScroll() {
        var y = window.scrollY || document.documentElement.scrollTop;
        if (y >= SHOW_AFTER_PX) setVisible(true);
        else if (y <= HIDE_ABOVE_PX) setVisible(false);
      }
      function dismiss() {
        sessionStorage.setItem(STORAGE_KEY, "1");
        setVisible(false);
      }
      var dismissBtn = banner.querySelector(".lm-sticky-banner__dismiss");
      if (dismissBtn) dismissBtn.addEventListener("click", dismiss);
      window.addEventListener("scroll", onScroll, { passive: true });
      onScroll();
    })();
  </script>
</Layout>
